data.description: Charming and Sunlit 3-Bedroom Home with Expansive Backyard Retreat  Welcome to your new haven of light and brightness! This delightful 3-bedroom, 1-bath home, freshly painted inside and out, with new vinyl flooring throughout, offers a perfect blend of comfort and potential.   Basement block freshly painted with a rubber Duck Coat.  New privacy cedar fence - freshly stained, concrete driveway, inside trim, bathroom vanity, ceiling fans, LED lighting, Wyoming blue rock landscaping, garden shed in backyard and one car garage shed.  Newer Refrigerator, Stove, Washer and Dryer.  Explore the possibilities of the unfinished basement—a blank canvas ready for your imagination.  Step outside into the expansive backyard, a private oasis surrounded by a sturdy privacy fence. The large yard invites outdoor activities, from gardening to family barbecues, offering a perfect extension of your living space.  Conveniently located near Sturgis Elementary School and Sturgis Middle School.
